'''''BGIS 2026: The Grind''''' is the official qualifcation event for Invited teams before the start of '''''Battlegrounds Mobile India Series (BGIS) 2026'''''.

==About==

===Format===
* '''BGIS 2026 - The Grind:''''' Jan 17th - Feb 1st, 2026
** 64 Invited Teams, 16 matchdays.
** Teams divided into 4 groups with 16 squads in each group.
** Each group will play 24 matches in respective weeks.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|'''All 64 teams'''}} based on the overall standings will seed to '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2026|BGIS 2026: Main Event]]'''

